instanceType.description: The instance type that the image version runs on. For valid values see [SageMaker Instance Types](https://docs.aws.amazon.com/sagemaker/latest/dg/notebooks-available-instance-types.html).

lifecycleConfigArn.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the Lifecycle Configuration attached to the Resource.

sagemakerImageArn.description: The ARN of the SageMaker image that the image version belongs to.

sagemakerImageVersionArn.description: The ARN of the image version created on the instance.
